      "name": "Martha",
      "comment": "Martha, it's a proper summer Tuesday out there \u2014 16 to 27\u00b0C, barely any wind, and the morning is wide open. If you can sneak out by six, the run is going to be gorgeous before it gets too warm. Afternoon's more of a cycling window if you feel like a longer ride \u2014 just slap on sunscreen, UV's creeping up around midday. Maybe convince Britt to join for a swim after."
    },
