      "comment": "Britt, Utrecht is handing you a perfect cycling evening on a plate \u2014 24\u00b0C, 10 km/h wind, dry. If you've got an early finish, get out by five and you'll have golden light the whole way. Alternatively, it's properly warm enough for a swim around lunchtime if you can swing it."
    }
